This mod is in the early testing phase, so please don't report bugs or tell me it doesn't work—I know that. It's just a pure alpha test, so most things don't work yet.
To spawn a random tank, press P. If your tank is destroyed, the game will crash—that's fine; you'd have to restart it anyway. Your tank doesn't have
armor, so don't count on it
